  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Choose a type of martial weapon. You understand how to use that type of martial weapon in combat.</em><br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You make attack rolls with the selected weapon normally (without the non-proficient penalty).<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>When using a weapon with which you are not proficient, you take a -4 penalty on attack rolls.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>Barbarians, fighters, paladins, and rangers are proficient with all martial weapons. They need not select this feat.<br/> You can gain Martial Weapon Proficiency multiple times. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a new type of weapon. ",
